# Theme-synced foundation assets — DO NOT FORMAT from inside this repo.
#
# shared/theme/manifest.mjs syncs these byte-for-byte into SEVEN surfaces and
# check-theme-drift.mjs compares them by sha256. Five of those surfaces live in
# OTHER repos (/var/www/signal, /var/www/retrospective, /var/www/scrumpoker,
# /var/www/raid, /var/www/plan), so reformatting the source here changes its hash
# and silently puts all five out of sync — each then needing its own commit and
# deploy to catch up. All eight copies are currently identical; keep them that way.
#
# Formatting these is a deliberate cross-repo exercise: format the source, run
# sync-theme, then commit and deploy every surface together. Until that happens
# they stay exactly as hand-written, and `--check` skips them rather than failing.
shared/theme/oscilloscope.js
hub/public/js/oscilloscope.js
marketing/public/js/oscilloscope.js
shared/theme/instrument-core.css
